earmarked for scholarships in natural and physical sciences 
he was very interested in the strength of our science and 
mathematics departments bronson said 
ernest cook sr vice president for physical affairs said the 
money will be used to fund about 10 full fouryear scholarships each 
year 
bronson solicitated the donation when he met cosby at a dinner 
party two months ago the college president said he was so 
persistent that cosby later joked he expected to find bronson hiding 
in his salad 
faculty members were stunned by news of the donation bronson 
said cosby had sworn him to secrecy 
